io.sphere.sdk.products.queries

Interface ProductQuery

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ExpansionPathContainer<Product>, MetaModelQueryDsl<Product,ProductQuery,ProductQueryModel,ProductExpansionModel<Product>>, MetaModelReferenceExpansionDsl<Product,ProductQuery,ProductExpansionModel<Product>>, PriceSelectionRequestDsl<ProductQuery>, Query<Product>, QueryDsl<Product,ProductQuery>, ReferenceExpansionDsl<Product,ProductQuery>, ReferenceExpansionSupport<Product>, ResourceQuery<Product>, SphereRequest<PagedQueryResult<Product>>

    public interface ProductQuery
extends MetaModelQueryDsl<Product,ProductQuery,ProductQueryModel,ProductExpansionModel<Product>>, PriceSelectionRequestDsl<ProductQuery>
    Provides a QueryDsl for products to formulate predicates, search expressions and reference expansion path expressions.

    For further information how to use the query API to consult the Query API documentation.
